    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://chicago.craigslist.org/chc/sec/6042744560.html"></div>
        </div>
DigiStream Investigations, Inc.<br>
Position: Field Investigator (Chicago, IL)<br>
Full-time, 40 hours per week minimum, 10 hours per day average<br>
Hourly Pay Rate: $14.00-$15.00 per hour<br>
First-year Total Compensation: $38,000-$42,000 first year total pay (entry-level), frequent overtime<br>
Applicants MUST reside in the greater Chicago region<br>
Benefits: Health, Dental, Vision, and Life insurance offered and 401(k) retirement plan with Company Match up to 4% offered<br>
Company vehicle provided, and you will be paid to commute to and from your cases<br>
<br>
DigiStream Investigations, Inc., a technology-centric private investigations firm, seeks a full-time Field Investigator to work under general supervision, investigating suspicious worker's compensation claims from various corporate clients in the Chicago region and surrounding areas.<br>
<br>
Duties including, but not limited to:<br>
Monitoring and videotaping various individuals as they conduct their normal day-to-day activities. Note-taking and detailed report rendering on the activities captured by the investigator.<br>
<br>
Requirements:<br>
Must possess Bachelor's Degree<br>
Must reside in the Chicago region<br>
Strong computer skills<br>
Ability to pass DMV, pre-employment physical and background check<br>
Ability to start work as early as 6:00am daily<br>
Must be a morning person<br>
Must be available to work weekends and most holidays<br>
Must possess critical-thinking skills<br>
Must be available to travel out of town for extended periods of time<br>
<br>
Candidate must have great intuition and the ability to process many mitigating factors during the course of the investigation. Decisions are expected to be made in an accurate and timely manner and in the best interest in preserving the confidentiality of the assignment in question.<br>
<br>
All equipment is provided including: a vehicle, company laptop, wi-fi access, a gas/maintenance card, and video equipment.<br>
<br>
Only apply if you can work a 5 day per week schedule, which includes weekends, with an average of 10 hours per day. You will be paid to commute to and from cases.<br>
<br>
No phone calls please. No resumes accepted at this time, only Employment Applications.<br>
<br>
Please fill out our online application at:<br>
<br>
www.digistream.com/Company-Info/Employment-Opportunities/Personal-Information    </section>

